ActElectoral Boundaries Readjustment Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of State (Federal Economic Development Agency for Southern Ontario) as the Minister for the Purposes of the Electoral Boundaries Readjustment Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2023-779 of July 26, 2023; and (2) designating the Minister of STATE (FEDERAL ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT AGENCY FOR SOUTHERN ONTARIO), a member of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the ELECTORAL BOUNDARIES READJUSTMENT ACT.
